PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of JAMES J. SMITH, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Morris Kaufman, who has resigned.
